\intbl\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb90\sa90\li45\ri45 It is player one\u8217?s turn and they choose move option 3 (cuirassier) from the queue, the piece in row 2 column 2 and decide to move it forward 2 squares.\par
\intbl\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb270\sa90\li45\ri45 Their score decreases by 7 as they chose the third move option in their queue.\par
