\intbl \cell
\intbl\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb90\sa90\li45\ri45 Player one decides to take the move option in the offer and replaces their ryott with a jazair.\par
\intbl\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb90\sa90\li45\ri45 This reduces their score by 8.\par
\intbl\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb90\sa90\li45\ri45 The offer is replenished by a randomly selected move option.\par
\intbl\f1\fs22\cf0\ltrpar\ql\sb90\sa90\li45\ri45 Taking the move option from the offer does not count as a move; their score is not increased even though their kotla is occupied.\par
